Package org.apache.logging.log4j.core.lookup

Class ConfigurationStrSubstitutor

java.lang.Object
org.apache.logging.log4j.core.lookup.StrSubstitutor
org.apache.logging.log4j.core.lookup.ConfigurationStrSubstitutor
All Implemented Interfaces:
ConfigurationAware, StringValueResolver
public final class ConfigurationStrSubstitutor extends StrSubstitutor
RuntimeStrSubstitutor is a StrSubstitutor which only supports recursive evaluation of lookups. This can be dangerous when combined with user-provided inputs, and should only be used on data directly from a configuration.
